{"tid":1615182,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「行動，目的，文宣」 缺一不可","createTime":"2019-10-03T04:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T07:02:06.000Z","uid":72879,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"08dbdd31c3a2b3e0b69c18dad2056704be3e5a64","tid":1615182,"uid":72879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:14:23.000Z","msg":"依兩日連登最多野關注扑爛舖頭，帶風向，之後先到中學生中槍，印尼女記者，國殤，黑記。<br />\n大家不如諗下會唔會錯配左資源，放太多心力落自我審查，咩野到底該做咩係唔該做呢？<br />\n<br />\n特意睇左好多個應唔應該扑爛舖頭既post 希望大家唔好將討論變成互罵, 然後變成互割 希望大家 be humble<br />\n<br />\n首先 標題適用於任何運動, 舉個例<br />\n觀塘大遊行 -&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\">行動</span><br />\n打爆燈柱 -&gt; 其中一個<span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span> 以表達香港既自由受到監控<br />\n非無理毀壞公物, 係因為自由受到監控, 政府既詭辯信服唔到群眾因而有是次行動 -&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\">文宣 </span><br />\n<br />\n到琴日講既藍絲舖頭, 點解有咁多爭議 其實係咪因為三環有野做得不足?<br />\n10月2遍地開花, 幫部份商店裝修 -&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\">行動</span><br />\n抗議黑警對學生開實彈,印尼女記者永久失明遊行 -&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣</span> -&gt; 裝修既原因, 有咩底線 e.g.不傷店員, 不搶劫, 不偷竊等等 (依樣亦可能暫時最缺乏而最需要令所有非同溫層/無上開連登既人緊貼番前線既作為)<br />\n<br />\n開緊post既同時亦見到下面巴打有個非常好既口號<br />\n例如 郭嘉巴打<br />\n&lrm;紅背景裝修、藍店罷買、黃店懲罰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1615026/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1615026/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n另外都係度講講, 希望手足唔好淨係識得文宣組做野 文宣組要點點點  希望大家都知道<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地每一個人都係文宣組, 文宣不足係我地每一個人既責任</span></strong> 你無設計既sense唔緊要, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最緊要係你有個心, 就算你渣住張白底黑字 都可以成為最強既文宣</span></strong><br />\n <br />\n黎緊請為印尼女記者發聲, 同埋為記者既專業行一次既感謝遊行  分唔分開兩次遊行就睇下大家想點<br />\n印尼女記者同感謝記者既遊行 -&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\">行動</span><br />\n令外國關注, 甚至由印尼相關機構對香港警察予以制裁-&gt;<span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣</span>-&gt;  以記者為題, 感謝記者既專業, 即使受到打壓仍不惜堅持為事件揭開真相, 日期, 時間, 地點, 等大家有共識即刻就宣傳"},{"pid":"1bc6988a09f18c2a39404715ae28fbe46f1e448f","tid":1615182,"uid":72879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:14:45.000Z","msg":"同意請分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de19d6cf0a936278bfccc376da610079cf025700","tid":1615182,"uid":211910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:15:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd90ed177d2898a4d3d81b6adcb18a1938764c48","tid":1615182,"uid":211910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:15:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3387bfcc0acc8e2311667139ee3e17311c752c8","tid":1615182,"uid":211910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:15:59.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"71041bc972e381895d5878aa37fa381d8056e0d5","tid":1615182,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jmPpQmD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjmPpQmD.jpg&h=d6ff1427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGZhqU0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGZhqU0.jpg&h=c882c645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WK0sN8k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWK0sN8k.jpg&h=a6ce104f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/unMvLU0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FunMvLU0.jpg&h=4eb221da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pNGSZe0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpNGSZe0.jpg&h=6012fecb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RUS3mtm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRUS3mtm.jpg&h=bfab3218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8y2B1G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8y2B1G.jpg&h=e1ab3886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CpMfW1L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?